profile:
OneTek Pest Solutions is a service provider for residential and commercial locations.  We have over 20 years experience in the GTA, Simcoe, and Muskoka area.  We focus on preventative maintenance solutions for customers to avoid costly and inconvenient repairs caused by insects and rodents.  We offer many programs including mosquito treatments to keep those annoying little insects away.
